---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import Container from "../../components/container.astro";
import JobApplicationForm from "../../components/jobapplicationform.astro";
---

<Layout title="Career">
  <Container>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">IT Business Analyst</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <div class="text-slate-700">
        <!-- <h2 class="font-medium text-2xl text-gray-800">Contact Nerd's House</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500 mt-3">
          Have something to say? We are here to help. Fill up the form or send
          email or call phone.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5"></div> -->

        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
          Nerd's House is looking for IT Business Analysts with basic UX
          concepts and has experience in handling clients and delivery.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
          The following qualities will help you to become a nerd.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc text-sm font-light pl-8 mb-4">
          <li>
            Strong understanding of the WordPress technology and related
            ecosystem
          </li>
          <li>
            Understand the Requirement of the Businesses and convert into Scope
            of work Document & Wireframes
          </li>
          <li>
            Knowledge about domain media publishing, performance marketing,
            e-commerce, paywall, monetisation tools, analytics tools, SEO
          </li>
          <li>Experience in managing customer deliveries end to end</li>
          <li>Experience in coordinating between clients and technical team</li>
          <li>
            Exceptional ability in requirement gathering and conducting
            meetings, presentations, discovery workshop with client and internal
            team
          </li>
          <li>
            Experience in tracking client feedback and initiating follow-up
            action.
          </li>
          <li>
            Knowledge in project planning & project documentation and creating
            the business estimate, proposal, SRS and questionnaire for clients.
          </li>
          <li>Good communication and coordination skills</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Why Nerd's House?</h2>

        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
          We have crafted our own culture and traditions in the past decade and
          the highlights are:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc text-sm font-light pl-8 mb-4">
          <li>Best employee benefits in the industry</li>
          <li>Performance appraisal twice a year</li>
          <li>Remote work option</li>
          <li>Great work-life balance</li>
          <li>Flexible leave policy</li>
          <li>Flat structure, zero micro-management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <JobApplicationForm />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a
        href="/career"
        class="bg-gray-100 px-5 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-200 transition"
        >‚Üê Back to Career</a
      >
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
